ETHICAL USAGE NOTICE:

This software is designed for educational and research purposes only. Users of
this software must comply with all applicable laws and regulations, including
but not limited to:

- Colombian Law 1273 of 2009 (Computer Crimes)
- Colombian Law 1581 of 2012 (Personal Data Protection)
- Colombian Law 1712 of 2014 (Transparency and Access to Public Information)
- Decree 1377 of 2013 (Data Protection Regulations)

The software includes an ethics module (ethical_compliance.py) that enforces:
- Domain whitelist (only minsalud.gov.co and datos.gov.co)
- Rate limiting (2 seconds minimum between requests)
- robots.txt verification
- Personal data detection
- Complete audit logging

Users must NOT use this software for:
- Unauthorized access to computer systems
- Collection of personal data without authorization
- Overloading or attacking servers
- Any illegal or unethical purposes

The authors are not responsible for misuse of this software. By using this
software, you agree to use it only for legitimate educational and research
purposes in compliance with all applicable laws.
